## When to Create New Folders

Create a new folder when:
- ‚úÖ You have 3+ related documents
- ‚úÖ A topic needs multiple supporting documents
- ‚úÖ Clear hierarchical relationship exists
- ‚úÖ You want to keep related research together

Don't create folders prematurely:
- ‚ùå Only 1-2 docs exist for a topic
- ‚ùå "Might need it later" (create when actually needed)
- ‚ùå Over-categorization (too many small folders)

